## @ConfigurationProperties

Bind a whole group of properties to a typed class:

```java
@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "app.payment")
@Validated
public class PaymentProperties {
    @NotNull
    private String apiUrl;

    @Min(1) @Max(60)
    private int timeoutSeconds = 30;

    private List<String> supportedCurrencies = List.of("USD", "EUR");

    // getters/setters
}

// Usage
@Service
public class PaymentService {
    public PaymentService(PaymentProperties props) {
        this.client = new HttpClient(props.getApiUrl(), props.getTimeoutSeconds());
    }
}
```
